    sequenceDiagram
        participant browser
        participant server

    		Note right of browser: The browser re-renders the page after the `submit` event is triggered
    		Note right of browser: Then, the `sendToServer` function initiates a POST request with the payload:
    		Note right of browser: {"content":"1","date":"2024-10-11T16:01:07.564Z"}
        browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
        activate server
        server-->>browser: JSON Response: {"message":"note created"}
        deactivate server
        Note right of browser: No further request is needed, since the page is not reloaded
